---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import posts from '../lib/blog-data.json';
import causes from '../lib/causes-data.json';
---

<Layout title="Home" description="Peace League Africa is building peace across 12 African countries through education, healthcare, clean water &amp; youth empowerment. Join 1,200+ volunteers. Donate today to transform conflict into lasting hope.">
  <Navigation />

  <main id="main-content">
    <section id="hero-section" class="relative text-white hero-gradient overflow-hidden min-h-[85vh] flex items-center">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 z-[1] opacity-[0.04] bg-[image:radial-gradient(circle_at_center,white_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:32px_32px]"></div>
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-hero-bg/60 via-transparent to-hero-bg/20 z-[2]"></div>
      <div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 h-32 bg-gradient-to-t from-hero-bg to-transparent z-[2]"></div>
      <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 lg:py-20 z-[3] w-full">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <div class="scroll-reveal mb-6">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-1.5 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-sm rounded-full text-sm font-medium text-accent-soft border border-white/10">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-accent animate-pulse"></span>
              12 Countries &middot; 500 Communities &middot; One Mission
            </span>
          </div>
          <h1 class="scroll-reveal text-[clamp(2.5rem,7vw,5rem)] font-bold leading-[1.02] tracking-[-2px] sm:tracking-[-3px] text-white">
            Turning Conflict<br/>
            <span class="text-accent">Into Lasting</span><br/>
            Peace
          </h1>
          <p class="scroll-reveal mt-6 sm:mt-8 text-lg sm:text-xl leading-relaxed text-white/70 max-w-2xl font-light [animation-delay:80ms]">
            From the classrooms of Nairobi to the refugee camps of South Sudan &mdash; we are an unstoppable movement of 1,200+ volunteers rebuilding communities torn apart by war, drought, and displacement.
          </p>
          <div class="scroll-reveal mt-10 sm:mt-12 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 sm:gap-6 [animation-delay:150ms]">
            <a href="/donate" class="group inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full sm:w-auto min-h-[56px] px-10 py-4 bg-accent text-on-dark font-semibold text-base rounded-full shadow-xl shadow-accent/25 hover:shadow-2xl hover:shadow-accent/40 hover:bg-accent-deep transition-all duration-300 ease-out-expo">
              Give Today
              <svg class="ml-2 w-5 h-5 transition-transform duration-300 group-hover:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
            </a>
            <a href="/causes" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full sm:w-auto min-h-[56px] px-10 py-4 border-2 border-white/25 text-white font-semibold text-base rounded-full hover:bg-white/10 hover:border-white/50 transition-all duration-300">
              Explore Our Causes
            </a>
          </div>
          <div class="scroll-reveal mt-12 sm:mt-16 flex items-center gap-8 sm:gap-12 text-white/60 [animation-delay:250ms]">
            <div class="flex -space-x-3">
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?w=48&h=48&fit=crop&crop=face&q=80" alt="" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-hero-bg" loading="lazy" />
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1531123897727-8f129e1688ce?w=48&h=48&fit=crop&crop=face&q=80" alt="" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-hero-bg" loading="lazy" />
              <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1517841905240-472988babdf9?w=48&h=48&fit=crop&crop=face&q=80" alt="" class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-hero-bg" loading="lazy" />
              <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full border-2 border-hero-bg bg-accent/20 flex items-center justify-center text-xs font-semibold text-accent-soft">1.2k+</div>
            </div>
            <div class="hidden sm:block w-px h-8 bg-white/10"></div>
            <p class="text-sm sm:text-base"><span class="text-white font-semibold">95%</span> of donations fund programs</p>
            <div class="hidden sm:block w-px h-8 bg-white/10"></div>
            <p class="text-sm sm:text-base"><span class="text-white font-semibold">45+</span> school programs</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 lg:py-20 bg-surface overflow-hidden">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="section-divider mb-6"></div>
        <h2 class="scroll-reveal text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold leading-[1.2] tracking-[-0.5px] text-ink text-center mb-4">Our Impact in Numbers</h2>
        <p class="scroll-reveal text-center text-lg text-steel max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-14">Grassroots peacebuilding measured in lives changed, communities rebuilt, and futures restored.</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 sm:gap-6 lg:gap-8">
          <div class="scroll-reveal group relative bg-canvas rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 border border-hairline text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-accent/20">
            <div class="absolute -top-3 -right-3 w-20 h-20 bg-accent/5 rounded-full blur-2xl"></div>
            <span class="big-stat-value text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-accent block leading-none" data-count-target="45" data-count-suffix="+">0</span>
            <span class="block mt-2 text-sm text-steel font-medium">Schools</span>
            <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-stone leading-relaxed">Peace education programs in 8 countries equipping the next generation of leaders.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="scroll-reveal group relative bg-canvas rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 border border-hairline text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-accent-warm/20" style="animation-delay: 80ms">
            <div class="absolute -top-3 -right-3 w-20 h-20 bg-accent-warm/5 rounded-full blur-2xl"></div>
            <span class="big-stat-value text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-accent-warm block leading-none" data-count-target="12" data-count-suffix="">0</span>
            <span class="block mt-2 text-sm text-steel font-medium">Countries</span>
            <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-stone leading-relaxed">From Kenya to DRC, we operate where conflict is deepest and hope is scarcest.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="scroll-reveal group relative bg-canvas rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 border border-hairline text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-accent/20" style="animation-delay: 150ms">
            <div class="absolute -top-3 -right-3 w-20 h-20 bg-accent/5 rounded-full blur-2xl"></div>
            <span class="big-stat-value text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-accent block leading-none" data-count-target="1200" data-count-suffix="+">0</span>
            <span class="block mt-2 text-sm text-steel font-medium">Volunteers</span>
            <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-stone leading-relaxed">Teachers, medics, engineers &mdash; everyday Africans building peace in their communities.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="scroll-reveal group relative bg-canvas rounded-2xl p-6 sm:p-8 border border-hairline text-center transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-accent-warm/20" style="animation-delay: 220ms">
            <div class="absolute -top-3 -right-3 w-20 h-20 bg-accent-warm/5 rounded-full blur-2xl"></div>
            <span class="big-stat-value text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold text-accent-warm block leading-none" data-count-target="95" data-count-suffix="%">0</span>
            <span class="block mt-2 text-sm text-steel font-medium">To Programs</span>
            <p class="mt-3 text-xs text-stone leading-relaxed">Every dollar donated goes directly to community-driven peacebuilding work.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 lg:py-20 bg-gradient-to-b from-canvas to-surface overflow-hidden">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="section-divider mb-6"></div>
        <h2 class="scroll-reveal text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold leading-[1.2] tracking-[-0.5px] text-ink text-center mb-4">Our Causes</h2>
        <p class="scroll-reveal text-center text-lg text-steel max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-14">Every cause is community-driven, locally led, and fully transparent. Here is where your support goes.</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
          {causes.slice(0, 6).map((cause, idx) => (
            <div class="scroll-reveal group bg-canvas rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-hairline shadow-sm transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-xl hover:border-accent/20" style={`animation-delay: ${idx * 80}ms`}>
              <div class="h-44 relative overflow-hidden">
                <img src={cause.image} alt={cause.title} width="400" height="220" class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 ease-out-expo group-hover:scale-105" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
                <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
                <span class="absolute bottom-3 left-3 badge-tag">{cause.category}</span>
              </div>
              <div class="p-5">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink leading-snug">{cause.title}</h3>
                <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-steel line-clamp-2 leading-relaxed">{cause.description}</p>
                <div class="mt-4">
                  <div class="flex justify-between text-sm mb-1.5">
                    <span class="font-semibold text-ink">${cause.raised_amount.toLocaleString()}</span>
                    <span class="text-stone">${cause.goal_amount.toLocaleString()}</span>
                  </div>
                  <div class="w-full bg-hairline rounded-full h-2 progress-track">
                    <div class="bg-accent h-2 rounded-full progress-bar" data-progress-width={Math.min((cause.raised_amount / cause.goal_amount) * 100, 100)} style="width: 0"></div>
                  </div>
                  <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-stone">{cause.donors_count} donors &middot; {Math.round((cause.raised_amount / cause.goal_amount) * 100)}% funded</p>
                </div>
                <a href={`/donate?cause=${encodeURIComponent(cause.name || '')}`} class="mt-4 inline-flex items-center justify-center w-full min-h-[44px] px-4 py-2.5 bg-primary text-on-dark text-sm font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-charcoal transition-all duration-300">
                  Donate to This Cause
                </a>
              </div>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
        <div class="mt-10 text-center">
          <a href="/causes" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center min-h-[44px] px-6 py-3 bg-primary text-on-dark font-medium text-sm rounded-full hover:bg-charcoal transition-colors">
            Explore All Causes
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 lg:py-20 bg-surface overflow-hidden">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="scroll-reveal text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold leading-[1.2] tracking-[-0.5px] text-ink text-center mb-4">How We Work</h2>
        <div class="section-divider mb-6"></div>
        <p class="scroll-reveal text-lg text-steel text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-14">A proven process rooted in listening, local leadership, and lasting change.</p>
        <div class="relative">
          <div class="hidden lg:block absolute top-24 left-[calc(16.66%+1.5rem)] right-[calc(16.66%+1.5rem)] h-0.5 bg-gradient-to-r from-accent/40 via-accent-warm/40 to-accent/40"></div>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 md:gap-6 lg:gap-12">
            <div class="scroll-reveal relative text-center md:text-left">
              <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-start gap-4 md:gap-5">
                <div class="flex-none w-14 h-14 bg-accent/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto md:mx-0">
                  <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4"/></svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2 justify-center md:justify-start">
                    <span class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-accent">Step 01</span>
                    <span class="hidden md:block w-8 h-px bg-accent/30"></span>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink">Assess &amp; Listen</h3>
                  <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-steel leading-relaxed">We spend months listening to communities before writing a single proposal. Local elders, teachers, and youth tell us what they actually need.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="scroll-reveal relative text-center md:text-left" style="animation-delay: 100ms">
              <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-start gap-4 md:gap-5">
                <div class="flex-none w-14 h-14 bg-accent-warm/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto md:mx-0">
                  <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-accent-warm" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"/></svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2 justify-center md:justify-start">
                    <span class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-accent-warm">Step 02</span>
                    <span class="hidden md:block w-8 h-px bg-accent-warm/30"></span>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink">Act Together</h3>
                  <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-steel leading-relaxed">We deploy resources directly &mdash; no middlemen, no overhead bloat. Local contractors, local materials, local pride in every well built and classroom furnished.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="scroll-reveal relative text-center md:text-left" style="animation-delay: 200ms">
              <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row md:items-start gap-4 md:gap-5">
                <div class="flex-none w-14 h-14 bg-accent-soft/20 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto md:mx-0">
                  <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-accent" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="1.5" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"/></svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2 justify-center md:justify-start">
                    <span class="text-xs font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase text-accent">Step 03</span>
                    <span class="hidden md:block w-8 h-px bg-accent/30"></span>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-ink">Sustain &amp; Hand Over</h3>
                  <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-steel leading-relaxed">We train local leaders to run every program themselves within 3 years. The best solutions come from within &mdash; we just help unlock them.</p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 lg:py-20 bg-canvas overflow-hidden">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="section-divider mb-6"></div>
        <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-14">
          <h2 class="scroll-reveal text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold leading-[1.2] tracking-[-0.5px] text-ink text-center mb-4">Your Donation Changes Lives</h2>
          <p class="scroll-reveal text-lg text-steel text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto">Every dollar goes directly to community-driven programs. Here is what your generosity makes possible.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
          <div class="scroll-reveal group relative p-6 rounded-2xl border border-hairline bg-surface transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-accent/30 overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute -top-8 -right-8 w-24 h-24 bg-accent/5 rounded-full blur-xl"></div>
            <div class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-accent mb-1 donation-amount" data-count-target="25" data-count-prefix="$">$25</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">Clean Water for a Family</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-steel leading-relaxed mb-4">Provides clean water for a family of five for one month, reducing waterborne disease and ending long walks to distant wells.</p>
            <div class="mt-auto">
              <div class="w-full bg-hairline rounded-full h-1.5 mb-3">
                <div class="bg-accent h-1.5 rounded-full" style="width: 62%"></div>
              </div>
              <a href="/donate?amount=25" class="btn-pulse-glow inline-flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-accent hover:text-accent-deep transition-colors group/btn">Donate Now <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1 transition-transform duration-200 group-hover/btn:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="scroll-reveal group relative p-6 rounded-2xl border border-hairline bg-surface transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-accent-warm/30 overflow-hidden" style="animation-delay: 80ms">
            <div class="absolute -top-8 -right-8 w-24 h-24 bg-accent-warm/5 rounded-full blur-xl"></div>
            <div class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-accent-warm mb-1 donation-amount" data-count-target="50" data-count-prefix="$">$50</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">Train a Peace Teacher</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-steel leading-relaxed mb-4">Equips an educator with conflict resolution curriculum and materials, reaching 100+ students with peace-building skills.</p>
            <div class="mt-auto">
              <div class="w-full bg-hairline rounded-full h-1.5 mb-3">
                <div class="bg-accent-warm h-1.5 rounded-full" style="width: 48%"></div>
              </div>
              <a href="/donate?amount=50" class="btn-pulse-glow inline-flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-accent-warm hover:text-amber-600 transition-colors group/btn">Donate Now <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1 transition-transform duration-200 group-hover/btn:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="scroll-reveal group relative p-6 rounded-2xl border border-hairline bg-surface transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-accent/30 overflow-hidden" style="animation-delay: 150ms">
            <div class="absolute -top-8 -right-8 w-24 h-24 bg-accent/5 rounded-full blur-xl"></div>
            <div class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-accent mb-1 donation-amount" data-count-target="100" data-count-prefix="$">$100</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">Sponsor a Child's Education</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-steel leading-relaxed mb-4">Covers school fees, books, and a uniform for one term, giving a child from a conflict-affected community a chance to learn and thrive.</p>
            <div class="mt-auto">
              <div class="w-full bg-hairline rounded-full h-1.5 mb-3">
                <div class="bg-accent h-1.5 rounded-full" style="width: 72%"></div>
              </div>
              <a href="/donate?amount=100" class="btn-pulse-glow inline-flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-accent hover:text-accent-deep transition-colors group/btn">Donate Now <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1 transition-transform duration-200 group-hover/btn:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="scroll-reveal group relative p-6 rounded-2xl border border-hairline bg-surface transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-2 hover:shadow-lg hover:border-accent-warm/30 overflow-hidden" style="animation-delay: 220ms">
            <div class="absolute -top-8 -right-8 w-24 h-24 bg-accent-warm/5 rounded-full blur-xl"></div>
            <div class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-accent-warm mb-1 donation-amount" data-count-target="500" data-count-prefix="$">$500</div>
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-ink mb-2">Community Reconciliation</h3>
            <p class="text-sm text-steel leading-relaxed mb-4">Funds a multi-day reconciliation workshop bringing together divided communities for dialogue, healing, and sustainable peace.</p>
            <div class="mt-auto">
              <div class="w-full bg-hairline rounded-full h-1.5 mb-3">
                <div class="bg-accent-warm h-1.5 rounded-full" style="width: 35%"></div>
              </div>
              <a href="/donate?amount=500" class="btn-pulse-glow inline-flex items-center text-sm font-medium text-accent-warm hover:text-amber-600 transition-colors group/btn">Donate Now <svg class="w-4 h-4 ml-1 transition-transform duration-200 group-hover/btn:translate-x-1" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-10 text-center">
          <p class="text-sm text-steel mb-5">Every contribution, no matter the size, creates ripples of peace that reach far beyond what any of us can imagine.</p>
          <a href="/donate" class="btn-pulse-glow inline-flex items-center justify-center min-h-[48px] px-8 py-3 bg-primary text-on-dark font-medium text-sm rounded-full hover:bg-charcoal transition-all duration-300 shadow-lg shadow-accent/20">
            Make a Donation
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-16 lg:py-20 bg-surface overflow-hidden">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="section-divider mb-6"></div>
        <h2 class="scroll-reveal text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-semibold leading-[1.2] tracking-[-0.5px] text-ink text-center mb-4">Trusted by Leading Organizations</h2>
        <p class="scroll-reveal text-center text-lg text-steel max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-4">We are proud to collaborate with these global and regional organizations committed to peace and sustainable development.</p>
        <p class="scroll-reveal text-center text-sm text-steel max-w-xl mx-auto mb-12">Together, we amplify our reach, share expertise, and ensure that every initiative is grounded in proven best practices.</p>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-3 md:grid-cols-6 gap-4">
